                  </svg>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <h4 class="text-sm font-medium text-gray-700">Address</h4>
                  <p class="text-gray-600">
                    Ehsan Seaview Hotel Sdn Bhd, No. 325, Batu 1, Jalan Rumah Rehat,
